## Source Ingestion
{% if include_agent_scaffold %}
To ingest source material into this vault, use the `/ingest-source` command. The workflow:
{% else %}
To ingest source material into this vault:
{% endif %}
1. Source material (chapter, wiki page, reference) goes into `sources/` as a source note
2. Entities are extracted and created/updated in `world/` using templates
3. Existing entities are updated additively (never overwrite user edits)
4. Wikilinks are created between related entities

When creating entities from source material, set `canon: true` and `source` to the attribution string. Set `genai: false` (the source is human-written, even if an agent does the extraction).
{% endif %}
